## Minimal change checklist (copy mentally)

**Property added/removed or renamed**  
→ **property-shortlist hub** · visit-guide · areas · investment · budget-financial · **builder-reputation** (north row) · **deep-eval** · full-evaluation (if present) · amenities/safety if that property had rows

**Price, all-in, possession, RERA, commute, address**  
→ **property-shortlist hub** · visit-guide · investment · budget-financial · **deep-eval** (all affected cells) · builder canvas only if narrative mentions that project

**External research pass (Reddit, portals, K-RERA notes)**  
→ **property-shortlist hub** (research column + Reddit table) · optional criteria canvas cross-link if methodology changes

**Criteria top 10 or visit-set (`C` rows) changes**  
→ **blr-property-criteria** (if ranking rules move) · **property-shortlist hub** (`track`) · **index.html** `PROPERTIES` · visit-guide · **deep-eval** if evidence rows shift

**Area / corridor thesis (e.g. STRR, new micro-market)**  
→ areas · investment · property-type-config (if hold/UDS story) · deep-eval area/connectivity/investment cells

**Builder landscape (new Tier 1/2, score edits, citywide note)**  
→ **builder-reputation** only (unless shortlist assigns a new builder — then also shortlist + deep-eval)

**Finishing a criterion write-up**  
→ the criterion canvas **and** matching cells in **deep-eval** (same response)

